      "text": [
        " اَلسَّمَاءِ ثَمَانِينَ ذِرَاعاً فَرَكِبَ فِيهَا فَطَافَتْ بِالْبَيْتِ سَبْعَةَ أَشْوَاطٍ وَ سَعَتْ بَيْنَ اَلصَّفَا وَ اَلْمَرْوَةِ سَبْعاً ثُمَّ «اِسْتَوَتْ عَلَى اَلْجُودِيِّ » »"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2277 - It has been narrated:\n\"The length of Noah's (as) ark was one thousand and two hundred cubits, its width was one hundred cubits, and its height into the sky was eighty cubits. He boarded it, and it circled the House (Kaaba) seven times and performed the sa'i (ritual walking) between Safa and Marwah seven times, and then it 'settled on Mount Judi.'\""
        ]
      }
    },
